    <description>
      EVERY-DAY is a beautiful, lightweight desktop workspace application for Windows 
      that helps you organize your daily notes, tasks, and thoughts.
      
      Features:
      - Multiple block types (Text, Checkbox, Header)
      - Section organization (Notes, ToDo, Tasks, Journal)
      - Dark/Light theme support
      - Auto-save functionality
      - Drag-and-drop reordering
      - System tray integration
      - Lightning fast startup
      - Local-first data storage
    </description>
    <summary>A beautiful, lightweight desktop workspace for Windows</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
      Version 1.0.0:
      - Initial release
      - Core functionality
      - Performance optimizations
      - Theme support
    </releaseNotes>
